{"tid":269324,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲教下我可以點","createTime":"2017-06-03T16:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T01:07:05.000Z","uid":99481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"859b9577f0e6b4bce457281abde01a1e476946b1","tid":269324,"uid":99481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:22:06.000Z","msg":"之前係學校有個女仔幾靚幾可愛<br />\n一開始我同佢都好岩傾<br />\n過左幾個月我就鐘意左佢<br />\n開始試下做D曖昧既野<br />\n有時帶嬲比佢著，食野會用紙巾幫佢抹嘴<br />\n果陣真係好開心，日日都好想陪係佢身邊<br />\n（其實到依家小弟都未追到佢）<br />\n但我知道佢身邊既人唔鐘意我，所以佢都開始慢慢遠離我，甚至依家想同佢傾計都冇機會傾到<br />\n其實咁係咪姐係我比人拒絕左呀？<br />\n有冇巴絲講下你地既想法，因為小弟真係唔知點，絲打如果個女係你，其實你諗緊啲咩？<br />\n求各位救下小弟，因為呢件事都唔開心左好耐，係咪我既錯呀？我係咪唔應該再諗點搵佢呀？"},{"pid":"1e20dbb8a4e7b1c467113707246d8010d6a27cfd","tid":269324,"uid":78683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:24:16.000Z","msg":"叫左你唔好咁厹嫁啦 又唔聽 那 出事啦 又開po問 一陣又要比人當狗咁撚啦"},{"pid":"74e88332c1d215fe596934787ce533ea944abcd5","tid":269324,"uid":71826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:30:08.000Z","msg":"朋友壓力好重要  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你冇行架喇"},{"pid":"7b91c90454a7a2643bacb3fa136afe20be261fd7","tid":269324,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:31:26.000Z","msg":"努力讀書啦....."},{"pid":"993723e28c98c9b0ffacf1b6b0da835e50916b6f","tid":269324,"uid":99481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:38:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫左你唔好咁厹嫁啦 又唔聽 那 出事啦 又開po問 一陣又要比人當狗咁撚啦</blockquote><br />\n真係冇做狗公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢段時間我做好本分，冇撩女仔，亦都冇隨便撩女仔架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b9e271914c947aef52438a152c63708f61353d","tid":269324,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:40:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫左你唔好咁厹嫁啦 又唔聽 那 出事啦 又開po問 一陣又要比人當狗咁撚啦</blockquote><br />\n真係冇做狗公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢段時間我做好本分，冇撩女仔，亦都冇隨便撩女仔架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比呢條link佢<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲教下我可以點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/269324/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/269324/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8399aa5103f1d0d79fd2eca6faf6dca05cebad77","tid":269324,"uid":60793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:40:13.000Z","msg":"唔好再著眼佢<br />\n著眼你自己去提升自己<br />\n要變靚仔 成績好  個人素養要提高"},{"pid":"d2afbc6f0fb5810cf7b7d1f608def03cf2367930","tid":269324,"uid":99481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T01:02:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朋友壓力好重要  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你冇行架喇</blockquote><br />\n情況真係壞到講下野都唔得呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想喊"},{"pid":"0a0a59628385a5937630245225eac374e73b0726","tid":269324,"uid":99481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T01:07:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好再著眼佢<br />\n著眼你自己去提升自己<br />\n要變靚仔 成績好  個人素養要提高</blockquote><br />\n因為佢係我全心全意鐘意既女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自問佢既事我都會幫佢打理，巴打有冇方法教下小弟呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我怕到我返返學果陣會好似行屍走肉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}